metadata.name: Samurai Robota #118
metadata.description:
In the Year 2250 robots were built with the latest technology, but their programming was based on the ancient codes of honor and duty of the samurai warriors of old. They were fierce fighters, equipped with powerful weapons and advanced sensors, but they were also deeply committed to the ideals of loyalty, courage, and self-sacrifice.
.
Robota by Hackerman
.
Samur-AI + Procreate + RoBot Urban Luts
